cdata.name: Experience Token
cdata.desc:
ExChain is a blockchain-based smart identity verification ecosystem offering to its users a unique and trustless smart identity. Within the ExChain ecosystem, users can exchange peer-to-peer data through the platform where both ends can verify Proof of Credibility, Self-analysis allowing cross-border hiring and job transfer.

EXT is the issued token by ExChain, built-on NEO's blockchain acting as GAS the fuel token. EXT is used to pay or to send rewards in ExChain's network.
